          "field_name": "application_method",
          "candidate_value": "Device means any electronic device that: \u2022 may be used to access our online platforms; \u2022 stores your Card, Card information, Credentials or PIN; \u2022 is registered to generate a Security Code; or \u2022 is associated with a phone number you registered to receive a Security Code.",
